The Appspec file used by CodeDeploy for an ECS deployment has the &#39;TaskDefinition&#39; parameter which specifies the exact task definition family name and revision [1]:

    TaskDefinition: &quot;arn:aws:ecs:us-east-1:111222333444:task-definition/my-task-definition-family-name:1&quot;

This should point to the new task definition you created for a new deployment.

